# Cloudflare Pages response headers
#
# This site uses fixed filenames (no content hashing), so HTML/CSS/JS
# must always be revalidated. Cloudflare returns a 304 Not Modified
# when nothing has changed â€” fast, but deploys are immediately visible.
#
# Images and video are safe for long cache: new uploads always get new
# filenames from the CMS, and video is replaced in-place rarely.
#
# Rules: last matching path wins.

/*
  Cache-Control: no-cache

/images/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=2592000

/blog/images/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=2592000

/my-tobago-guide/images/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=2592000

/i-am-tobago/images/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=2592000

/my-tobago-guide/hero-bg.mp4
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=2592000
